{"tid":1046954,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我個frd日日番學都望住我下體","createTime":"2019-03-04T15:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T16:15:36.000Z","uid":218575,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad3cc784dc0d6a93093c447efc9802b230b673d","tid":1046954,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"話說我第一日番學識咗個朋友<br />\n咁一開始佢都正正常常 幾好無乜野 <br />\n但識耐咗發現佢成日無啦啦望住我下體<br />\n我都百分之九十九點九九肯定佢係望住我下體<br />\n<br />\n今日上堂佢全程偷偷地係咁望<br />\n平時去廁所仲癡線 佢望實唔郁<br />\n搞到我去廁所都驚驚地 <br />\n<br />\n今日再去廁所 佢望住我碌鳩<br />\n陰陰嘴笑 仲伸條脷出黎<br />\n我嚇到即刻鳩縮 尿都唔屙走人 <br />\n<br />\n點算好 好驚下次去廁所佢沖埋黎幫我含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfd7517fdf41077ad1d4b0c7b8fe5163940e36f","tid":1046954,"uid":190714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"岩啦 咁咪有自信囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fc9deca9e6651f826849e4b2585b023ea58f1f","tid":1046954,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"報串俾女老師知有人想含你"},{"pid":"393fe47715d98884309bf9b6a98649bce62865d3","tid":1046954,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:47:16.000Z","msg":"假膠黎講.txt"},{"pid":"a23143b9679bfa1933c4af213f05460c3fdebc4c","tid":1046954,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cfd7517fdf41077ad1d4b0c7b8fe5163940e36f","tid":1046954,"uid":190714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"岩啦 咁咪有自信囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"a96a54fe641eee36c9c7d97e1bb1192fab5f7362","tid":1046954,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61fc9deca9e6651f826849e4b2585b023ea58f1f","tid":1046954,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc